-----Input:-----
- First-line will contain $T$, the number of test cases. Then the test cases follow. 
- Each test case contains a single line of input,$N$. 

-----Output:-----
For each test case, output in a single line answer 1 or 0.

-----Constraints-----
- $1 \leq T \leq 10^6$
- $1 \leq N \leq 10^6$

-----Sample Input:-----
2
19
385

-----Sample Output:-----
0
1
